$ Oracle: DBA_TAB_COMMENTS
@ dba_tab_comments

`dba_tab_comments` records comments for → development/databases/Oracle/objects/tables[tables] and
→ development/databases/Oracle/objects/views[views].

Such comments can be stored with the `→ development/databases/Oracle/SQL/statement/verbs/comment` SQL verb.

sa:
  Comments on → development/databases/Oracle/objects/tables/columns[columns] (of tables and views) are record in  `→ development/databases/Oracle/installed/data-dictionary/col/comments`.
